item_prototype.name: Incoming broadcast/multicast traffic on interface $1
item_prototype.description: The number of non-unicast (i.e., subnetwork- broadcast or subnetwork-multicast) packets delivered to a higher-layer protocol.

item_prototype.name: Incoming traffic on interface $1
item_prototype.description: The number of octets in valid MAC frames received on this interface, including the MAC header and FCS.

item_prototype.name: Incoming unicast traffic on interface $1
item_prototype.description: The number of subnetwork-unicast packets delivered to a higher-layer protocol.

item_prototype.name: Outgoing broadcast/multicast traffic on interface $1
item_prototype.description: The total number of packets that higher-level protocols requested be transmitted, and which were addressed to a multicast or broadcast address at this sub-layer, including those that were discarded or not sent.

item_prototype.name: Outgoing traffic on interface $1
item_prototype.description: The number of octets transmitted in MAC frames on this interface, including the MAC header and FCS.

item_prototype.name: Outgoing unicast traffic on interface $1
item_prototype.description: The total number of packets that higher-level protocols requested be transmitted, and which were not addressed to a multicast or broadcast address at this sub-layer, including those that were discarded or not sent.
